USER
	-User Id
	-List of Tweets
	-List of Users followed
	
USER CONTROLLER LAYOUT

	//Get all users - GetMapping("/users")
		
	//Get one user - GetMapping("/users/{id}")
	
	//ADD NEW USER - GetMapping("/users/add") 


TWEET
	-tweet id
	-description
	-timestamp - @JsonIgnore - to hide in the response

TWEET CONTROLLER LAYOUT

	//User can post  a tweet - POST/users/{userId}/tweet
	
	
	//User can retrieve his own tweets - GET/users/{userId}/tweets
	
	
	//User can follow others - POST/users/{userid}/follow/{userId}
	
	
	//User can Retrieve all followed Users - GET/users/{userId}/following
	
	
	//User can Retrieve all the tweets by the ones he's following in chronological order - GET/users/{userId}/wall